(1) Ditmas Ave., at its intersection with Canarsie Lane and Ralph Ave., showing the Wyckoff house in the background, and to the left foreground, is one of the Brooklyn Union Gas Co. plants.

October 1928.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(2) The same, viewed in the opposite direction, showing in the background fuel tanks of the Superior Coal Co.

October 1928.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(3) The same, showing a close rear view.

April 1929.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.

(4) The same, showing a front view.

April 1929.

Eugene L. Armbruster Collection.
